            "title": "迅銷午後停牌待發業績公告",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">迅銷(06288)發公告，表示股份將於下午短暫停牌，待發截至今年2月底止半年中期業績公告。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851420-%e8%bf%85%e9%8a%b7%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%81%9c%e7%89%8c%e5%be%85%e7%99%bc%e6%a5%ad%e7%b8%be%e5%85%ac%e5%91%8a",
