        {
            "title": "騰訊雲5月9日起將AI算力等產品服務加價5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)旗下騰訊雲宣布，鑑於5月9日起對AI算力等相關產品及服務，加價5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251111_FI_source-web_00700-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/20251111_FI_source-web_00700-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊雲表示，今次加價是鑑於全球AI算力需求持續激增，核心硬件供應鏈成本大幅上漲，為保障服務質量及算力資源的持續供給，決定在5月9日凌晨起，對AI算力、容器服務及彈性MapReduce (EMR)相關產品刊例價進行調整。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">根據公布，騰訊雲的AI算力相關產品服務、容器服務TKE-原生節點相歇產品服務、彈性MapReduce (EMR)相關產品服務，價格均上調5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">對於在2月9日之前已購買相關產品及服務的客戶，當前訂單或計費周期內價格不受影響，新價格將在下一個續費周期生效。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851389-%e9%a8%b0%e8%a8%8a%e9%9b%b25%e6%9c%889%e6%97%a5%e8%b5%b7%e5%b0%87ai%e7%ae%97%e5%8a%9b%e7%ad%89%e7%94%a2%e5%93%81%e6%9c%8d%e5%8b%99%e5%8a%a0%e5%83%b95",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240814_FI_source-web_00700-LA-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 13:02:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "珀麗灣唯一500萬元內兩房放盤     460萬元成交減價15萬元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中原地產珀麗灣分行新近促成珀麗灣22座低層H室成交，單位實用面積490平方呎，兩房間隔，享園景，開價475萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">區內分支家庭眼見屋苑500萬元內兩房放盤已無其它選擇，於復活節長假期積極議價洽購上址，經過多日議價後，最終減價15萬元，以460萬元成交，實用呎價9388元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">原業主於2018年4月以580萬元買入，持貨約8年，賬面蝕120萬元，貶值21%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">屋苑本月暫錄得2宗買賣成交，平均實用呎價10309元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851249-%e7%8f%80%e9%ba%97%e7%81%a3%e5%94%af%e4%b8%80500%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e5%85%a7%e5%85%a9%e6%88%bf%e6%94%be%e7%9b%a4-460%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4%e6%b8%9b%e5%83%b915%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 12:32:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "半日收市︱略作回吐 恒指跌91點報25801點 阿里、小米拖大市後腿",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">市場觀望中東局勢發展，港股今早跟隨外圍略作回吐。重磅股個別發展，阿里巴巴(09988)與小米(01810)均有份拖大市後腿。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早低開136點，初段跌幅曾擴大至239點，見25653點即現反彈，中段最高曾見25852點，僅跌40點，其後跌幅一度重新擴大至過百點，尾市跌勢稍為收斂；恒指中午收報25801點，跌91點或0.35%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"迅策招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"迅策招股書封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">迅策招股書封面</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20250526_FI_source-ap_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"迅策招股書封面\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">迅策招股書封面</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，半日跌62點或1.26%，報4861點；國企指數跌38點或0.45%，報8638點。主板半日成交縮減至1266.52億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指半日跌137點，報25811點，高水9點。科指期貨跌76點，報4866點，高水5點。國指期貨跌57點，報8641點，高水2點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅科股個別發展，阿里巴巴與小米成為拖低恒指點數最多兩隻股份，其中阿里巴巴獲多家券商發報告點評，儘管投資評級依然正面，但亦有部份券商趁機調低對該股目標價。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">富瑞便將阿里巴巴目標價由206元降至179元，認為集團旗下淘天針對核心商家推商務發展計畫提供的補貼，再加上千問App在農曆年期間推廣活動的支出，難免令集團季度在「其他業務」分部的卜虧損增加；瑞銀更將該股目標價由185元降至166元，評級維持「買入」；摩根大通在維持對該股「增持」評級的同時，則把目標價由200元降至195元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">阿里巴巴今早股價全程報跌，高位123.9元時仍跌2.06%；中午收報123元，跌2.77%，單一股份已令恒指跌逾53點。小米今早亦受壓，半日高位32.34元時仍跌1.28%；中午收報31.72元，跌3.18%，亦拖低恒指30點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/20250807_FI_source-web_09988.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：阿里巴巴官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，「ATMXJ」其餘3位成員則低開高走，半日全部轉升收市，當中以近期持續回購的騰訊(00700)表現最佳，半日升0.89%，報512.5元；美團(03690)微升0.06%，報88.55元；京東(09618)亦升0.27%，報112.2元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不少新興熱門科股今早也持續造好，被視為「Token第一股」的迅策(03317)便再破頂創歷史新高，半日漲15.58%，報268.6元。兩隻AI大模型股亦炒上，智譜(02513)同樣破頂，中午收報982.5元，升13.13%；MiniMax(00100)剛發布命令行工具MMX-CLI，股價重越千元關口，中午收報1036元，升3.7%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"迅策招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"迅策招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">迅策招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國乘聯會最新收據顯示，4月份首6日全國乘用車市場新能源零售按年跌24%，內地車股今早卻個別發展。吉利汽車(00175)創逾3年新高，半日升2.69%，報24.46元；比亞迪(01211)則跌3.37%，報103.2元。「蔚小理」兩跌一升，小鵬汽車(09868)跌3.89%，報68元；理想汽車(02015)跌0.68%，報72.8元；蔚來(09866)逆市升3.45%，報52.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">本地藍籌地產股升多於跌，領展(00823)宣布以溢價售新加坡零售物業後今早裂口向上，中午收報38.36元，升1.75%，創1個月新高；恒基地產(00012)也升1.4%，報30.4元；新鴻基地產(00016)升0.36%，報138.8元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不少盈喜股也受捧，中國鋁業(02600)升3.15%，報12.79元；中偉新材(02579)漲1.6%，報36.94元，見1個月新高。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851185-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e7%95%a5%e4%bd%9c%e5%9b%9e%e5%90%90-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c91%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125801%e9%bb%9e-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e3%80%81%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e6%8b%96",
